# unit/

BATS test suite for Intent CLI covering command routing, project initialization, steel thread and work package management, skill/agent systems, and CLI utilities. All tests use shared test helpers and sandbox environments to ensure isolation and repeatability.

## Files

- `basic.bats` -- Test infrastructure verification and helper function validation
- `config.bats` -- Configuration loading, PROJECT_ROOT detection, legacy structure support
- `global_commands.bats` -- Global commands (help, version, doctor, info, bootstrap) that work anywhere
- `bootstrap.bats` -- Bootstrap command for initial Intent setup and ~/.config/intent initialization
- `init_commands.bats` -- Project initialization with directory structure and config.json creation
- `project_commands.bats` -- Project detection and project-context-dependent commands
- `st_commands.bats` -- Steel thread lifecycle (create, list, show, start, complete)
- `wp_commands.bats` -- Work package management within steel threads
- `agent_commands.bats` -- Claude subagent system with install/sync/list/status operations
- `skills_commands.bats` -- Claude skill installation, listing, syncing, and status tracking
- `help_commands.bats` -- Help system and command documentation display
- `treeindex_commands.bats` -- Treeindex generation with flags and directory processing
- `fileindex_commands.bats` -- Fileindex generation with filtering and output options
- `test_autopsy.bats` -- Intent-autopsy skill full directory install and scripts verification
- `test_diogenes.bats` -- Diogenes subagent and intent-elixir-testing skill integration
